## Tech Stack

- **Backend**: FastAPI (Python)
- **Frontend**: Gradio
- **Package Manager**: uv
- **Deployment**: Hugging Face Spaces

## Run Locally

```bash
# Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/jihane01/GetFarmPOC.git
cd GetFarmPOC

# Install uv
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh

# Install dependencies
uv sync

# Run API (terminal 1)
uv run getfarm-api

# Run Gradio app (terminal 2)
uv run getfarm-app
